<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 03:14:49 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>NTV称，日本首相考虑在地震警告后取消中亚之行</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japans-pm-weighs-cancelling-central-asia-trip-after-earthquake-warning-ntv-says-2024-08-09/</link><description>据日本电视台报道，日本首相岸田文雄正在考虑取消原定于周五至周一访问哈萨克斯坦、乌兹别克斯坦和蒙古的计划，此前气象官员表示发生大地震的风险高于平常。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 03:06:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japans-pm-weighs-cancelling-central-asia-trip-after-earthquake-warning-ntv-says-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市将以高位结束残酷的一周，日元承压</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-08-09/</link><description>亚洲股市在高位结束了艰难的一周，日本股市即将收复周一以来的所有巨额跌幅，而日元再次下滑，因为市场削弱了美国大幅降息的可能性。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 02:19:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>天气影响导致中国消费价格上涨，但内需依然疲软</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-july-consumer-prices-jump-faster-than-expected-producer-deflation-2024-08-09/</link><description>7月份中国消费者价格上涨速度略快于预期，部分原因是天气因素影响了食品供应，而生产者通货紧缩持续存在，使中国的基本消费趋势保持疲软，这是对政策制定者的考验。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 01:37:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-july-consumer-prices-jump-faster-than-expected-producer-deflation-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>由于就业救济，美元接近一周高点；日元贬值</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-near-one-week-high-jobs-relief-yen-sags-2024-08-09/</link><description>周五，美元兑主要竞争对手徘徊在一周高点附近，此前美国初请失业金人数出现近一年来最大跌幅，缓解了人们对迫在眉睫的经济衰退的担忧。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 01:18:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-near-one-week-high-jobs-relief-yen-sags-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>官方媒体称交易账户不得借用，中国国债下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-bond-trading-accounts-must-not-be-borrowed-or-transferred-state-media-2024-08-09/</link><description>监管机构对中国炙手可热的债券市场涉嫌不当行为展开调查后，官方媒体表示交易账户不得借用或转让，中国国债周五下跌。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 00:59:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-bond-trading-accounts-must-not-be-borrowed-or-transferred-state-media-2024-08-09/</guid></item><item><title>大熊猫栖息地在加州动物园大张旗鼓地开放</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/giant-panda-habitat-opens-california-zoo-much-fanfare-2024-08-08/</link><description>周四，圣地亚哥动物园的两只中国大熊猫在一场国际仪式上向公众开放，两只中国大熊猫现已成为加州居民。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 23:05:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/giant-panda-habitat-opens-california-zoo-much-fanfare-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：乐观情绪上升，但中国通胀迫在眉睫</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-08-08/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 21:48:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>加拿大和澳大利亚瞄准中国，表示加强军事合作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/canada-australia-eyeing-china-signal-more-military-cooperation-2024-08-08/</link><description>加拿大和澳大利亚对中国对南海争议海域的主权声索表示震惊，周四表示，两国将加强军事和国防工业合作。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 21:42:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/canada-australia-eyeing-china-signal-more-military-cooperation-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>咖啡贸易商 NKG 进军中国以满足不断增长的需求</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/coffee-trader-nkg-expands-into-china-tap-surging-demand-2024-08-08/</link><description>全球最大的咖啡贸易商之一、德国咖啡贸易商 Neumann Kaffee Gruppe (NKG) 周四表示，该公司已在中国开设了一家子公司，希望满足亚洲增长最快的咖啡市场对咖啡豆不断增长的需求。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 21:00:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/coffee-trader-nkg-expands-into-china-tap-surging-demand-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>通用汽车表示尽管面临挑战仍致力于中国业务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/gm-says-it-is-committed-china-operations-despite-challenges-2024-08-08/</link><description>通用汽车周四表示，尽管面临来自本土品牌的激烈竞争，该公司仍致力于在中国建立盈利且自我可持续的业务。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 16:16:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/gm-says-it-is-committed-china-operations-despite-challenges-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>举重-中国小将罗夺得女子59公斤级金牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/weightlifting-luo-china-wins-womens-59kg-gold-medal-2024-08-08/</link><description>中国小将罗世芳周四在巴黎奥运会上以241公斤的总成绩夺得59公斤级奥运会举重冠军，刷新了抓举和挺举的奥运纪录。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 15:14:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/weightlifting-luo-china-wins-womens-59kg-gold-medal-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>谢跳水跳板金牌卫冕让中国队一路横扫</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/diving-chinas-xie-wins-mens-three-metre-springboard-gold-2024-08-08/</link><description>中国选手谢思怡在东京奥运会上获得最高荣誉后，阔别跳水项目两年，周四在巴黎奥运会上成功卫冕三米板跳水金牌。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 14:33:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/diving-chinas-xie-wins-mens-three-metre-springboard-gold-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>美国因强迫维吾尔人劳动而禁止另外五家中国公司进口</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/society-equity/us-bans-imports-five-more-chinese-companies-over-uyghurs-2024-08-08/</link><description>据政府发布的消息称，美国周四因涉嫌侵犯维吾尔人人权而禁止另外五家中国公司进口产品，这是其从美国供应链中消除强迫劳动制造的商品的努力的一部分。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 13:38:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/society-equity/us-bans-imports-five-more-chinese-companies-over-uyghurs-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国电动汽车制造商比亚迪推出首款配备激光雷达传感器的车型</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-ev-maker-byd-launches-first-model-with-lidar-sensor-2024-08-08/</link><description>中国电动汽车（EV）巨头比亚迪周四推出了新版Seal EV，这是该公司首款配备激光雷达传感器的车型。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 13:26:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-ev-maker-byd-launches-first-model-with-lidar-sensor-2024-08-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国明阳签署意大利风力涡轮机工厂协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinas-mingyang-signs-italy-wind-turbine-plant-deal-2024-08-08/</link><description>意大利工业部周四表示，中国明阳智能能源公司、意大利能源公司Renexia和意大利工业部已签署建立风力涡轮机制造厂的协议。</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 12:18:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinas-mingyang-signs-italy-wind-turbine-plant-deal-2024-08-08/</guid></item></channel></rss>